snippet.title: Georg He personal video
snippet.description:
Hello~ Hello everyone, Tuesday
Our game will be officially launched on July 17 (that is, this Friday!)! !
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1254900/The_Vigilant_Villa/
Today I bring you a personal introduction of the character Georg He in the game~
I hope you like it
(I know boss Georg He is actually quite popular~!)
